Token.Abstract: Returns a dictionary with all the data of the measurement characteristic minus the flags, size, and E2E-CRC (if present). Keys and enumerations are defined in the CGMConstants.h file, which is imported with this category.

Parameter.Name: crcPresent
Parameter.Abstract: Indicates whether the characteristic includes the E2E-CRC field

ReturnValue.Abstract: All the data of the measurement characteristic minus the flags, size, and E2E-CRC (if present). Keys and enumerations are defined in the CGMConstants.h file, which is imported with this category.

Token.Abstract: Returns a dictionary with the supported features and the glucose concentration fluid type and sample location. Keys, enumerations, and values are defined in the CGMConstants.h file, which is imported with this category.

ReturnValue.Abstract: All the supported features and the glucose concentration fluid type and sample locaiton.

Token.Abstract: Returns a dictionary with the current status of the CGM sensor. Structure is the same as in the measurement characteristic. Keys and enumerations are defined in the CGMConstants.h file, which is imported with this category.

Parameter.Name: crcPresent
Parameter.Abstract: crcPresent Indicates whether the characteristic includes the E2E-CRC field

ReturnValue.Abstract: The current status of the cgm sensor

Token.Abstract: Session start time is the time the last session started

Parameter.Name: crcPresent

ReturnValue.Abstract: The date of the current CGM session start time

Token.Abstract: Session run time is the time offset from the session start time when the sensor should be replaced

ReturnValue.Abstract: The time offset of the CGM sensor run time. Offset is from the CGM Session start time
